{"title":"抗击非典","authors":["郑剑"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":5,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗击非典"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郑剑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江南莺飞北国暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华夏无处不春天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正当征途迈新步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突降病魔名非典。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞爪猖狂施恶手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张牙狰狞垂毒涎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隐迹秽污多变异，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏身飞沫可传染。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无心遇袭罹疫疾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恣意横行欲蔓延。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场斗争悄然起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同样争夺无硝烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵挂民瘼急划策，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"统揽全局果决断。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋然抗击为大事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迅速行动莫迁延。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身先士卒呈风骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柱石中流见肝胆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“揪心”之语情切切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“坦诚”二字意拳拳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无形长城新筑起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一方有难八方援。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万众一心聚伟力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众志成城抗非典。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白衣战士舍生死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"科研尖兵肩并肩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争分夺秒救危弱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千方百计擒凶顽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党群火线写忠诚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"官民战地共苦甘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身负重托不退缩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越是艰险越向前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从来真金出烈火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岂有松柏畏严寒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"优良传统光日月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族精神续新篇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人谓多难可兴邦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厥我中华压不弯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且待除魔得胜时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再送瘟神烧纸船。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":15,"page_end":15}